CISDID + Cambridge Italian Dialect Syntax Meeting 
Short Title: CISDID + CIDSM in Italy 

Date: 04-Jul-2008 - 06-Jul-2008 
Location: Pescara, Italy 
Contact: Roberta D'Alessandro 
Contact Email: r.a.g.dalessandro@let.leidenuniv.nl 
Meeting URL: http:// 

Linguistic Field(s): General Linguistics; Historical Linguistics; Morphology;
Syntax 

Subject Language(s): Italian (ita)

Meeting Description: 

This conference aims at bringing together scholars working on Italian and
Italian dialects, to constitute a common platform for discussion and develop an
interdisciplinary approach to the study of these subjects. 

Pescara, Museo delle Genti d'Abruzzo
4-6 July 2008

Università D'Annunzio
Fondazione Giammarco
Cambridge University
Laboratoire de recherche sur les asymétries d'interfaces, Université du Québec à
Montreal
Regione Abruzzo
Città di Pescara

Are happy to announce the inaugural conference for the:
CISDID
Centro Internazional per lo Studio e la Didattica dell'Italiano e Dei Dialetti
International centre for the study and diffusion of Italian and Italian dialects
and the
CIDSM in Italy
Cambridge Italian Dialect Syntax Meeting in Italy

There will be two main workshops: 

1.	
L'italiano oggi / Italian today

Invited speakers:

Andrea Gareffi
Claudio Giovanardi
Pietro Trifone
Diego Poli

2.
Morfosintassi dei dialetti italiani - CIDSM in Italy / Morpho-syntax of Italian
dialects - CIDSM in Italy

Invited speakers:

Cecilia Poletto
Jean-Yves Pollock
Leonardo Savoia
Raffaella Zanuttini

A call for paper for both workshops will be out soon. 

Conference organizing committee

Roberta D'Alessandro
Anna Maria Di Sciullo
Marilena Giammarco
Adam Ledgeway
Mario Saltarelli
Antonio Sorella






